[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Plan-document RAG with strict version scoping correctly elevated.** Step 4A `plan_document_retrieval_tool.invoke({...plan_id: session.plan_context.plan_id, plan_year: session.plan_context.plan_year, document_types_in_scope: [...], top_k: 8})` enforces plan-and-year scoping at retrieval time. Step 4D citations carry document_version, section_id, effective_date.
