[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Provider-network-lookup with rendering-vs-facility distinction correctly elevated.** Step 5A `provider_network_lookup_tool.invoke({..., include_ancillary_services: true})` and Step 5C compose_network_status_response includes `ancillary_warning_applies` and `no_surprises_act_applicable`. This is the recipe-distinct No-Surprises-Act-aware architectural primitive.
